```

### Lemmatization

```python
from bgnlp import LemmaTaggerConfig, LemmaTagger

lemma = LemmaTagger(config=LemmaTaggerConfig())
text = "Добре дошли!"
print(lemma(text))
```

```bash
[{'word': 'Добре', 'lemma': 'Добре'}, {'word': 'дошли', 'lemma': 'дойда'}, {'word': '!', 'lemma': '!'}]
```


